title: Week 11 Red Challenge Flag Picks & Dolphins CB Xavien Howard
itunes:title: Week 11 Red Challenge Flag Picks & Dolphins CB Xavien Howard
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined in Studio 66 alongside Handsome Hank & Matt "Money" Smith to preview Week 11 of the NFL. The guys get into Le'Veon Bell officially not reporting to the Steelers and giving their picks as to where he will play next season (7:15). Next, Money and Eddie Spaghetti argue over Notre Dame vs Syracuse and the Fightin' Irish being in the college football playoff, Money also reads one of Spaghetti's Tweets (15:45). Then the trio gave their Week 11 Red Challenge Flag picks for the five biggest games of this week (30:40). Finally, Miami Dolphins standout corner back, Xavien Howard, comes in studio to kibitz with Shek & our resident Dolphins fan Handsome Hank (42:43).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
